The SDGs in the City Program is an ambitious plan to provide opportunities to different parts of the New York City community to implement the SDGs locally. We aim to give them the knowledge and encouragement they need to make sustainable changes in their personal and professional lives. We are currently organizing around three streams of work through which New Yorkers can learn about and implement the SDGs.
